        <item>
        <title>忆光75</title>
        <link>https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 22 Jun 2023 21:14:20 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/photos/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%981.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 忆光75" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;摊牌了，冲这颜值买的&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
键盘：忆光75V6 青春版&lt;br&gt;
套件为光头75V3，键帽为全透MDA高度球帽&lt;br&gt;
轴为灰木轴V3，自带厂润&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%982.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1920&#34;
	height=&#34;1162&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%982_huc34067c74a4a7ad565b0929c68c1b567_100887_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%982_huc34067c74a4a7ad565b0929c68c1b567_100887_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;背部展示&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;165&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;396px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
非常喜欢这个旋钮设计，虽然不会有很大的功能性，但是使得键盘单调的板块变得有趣味性
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%983.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1920&#34;
	height=&#34;971&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%983_hue84307bc8e6b9f26adbd4a20afa23313_159622_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://ClimbingMouse.github.io/p/%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%983_hue84307bc8e6b9f26adbd4a20afa23313_159622_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;侧面展示&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;197&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;474px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
